#. type: Title ===
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/security-authentication-mechanisms.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "OpenID Connect client and filters"
msgstr "Cliente e filtros OpenID Connect"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/security-authentication-mechanisms.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The `quarkus-oidc-client` extension provides `OidcClient` for acquiring and refreshing access tokens from OpenID Connect and OAuth2 providers that support the following token grants:"
msgstr "A extensão `quarkus-oidc-client` fornece o `OidcClient` para adquirir e atualizar tokens de acesso de provedores OpenID Connect e OAuth2 que suportam as seguintes concessões de token:"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/security-authentication-mechanisms.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`client-credentials`"
msgstr "`client-credentials`"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/security-authentication-mechanisms.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`password`"
msgstr "`password`"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/security-authentication-mechanisms.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`refresh_token`"
msgstr "`refresh_token`"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/security-authentication-mechanisms.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The `quarkus-resteasy-client-oidc-filter` extension requires the `quarkus-oidc-client` extension.\n"
"It provides JAX-RS RESTful Web Services `OidcClientRequestFilter`, which sets the access token acquired by `OidcClient` as the `Bearer` scheme value of the HTTP `Authorization` header.\n"
"This filter can be registered with MicroProfile REST client implementations injected into the current Quarkus endpoint, but it is not related to the authentication requirements of this service endpoint.\n"
"For example, it can be a public endpoint or be protected with mTLS."
msgstr ""
"A extensão `quarkus-resteasy-client-oidc-filter` requer a extensão `quarkus-oidc-client`.\n"
"Ela fornece o `OidcClientRequestFilter` do JAX-RS RESTful Web Services, que define o token de acesso adquirido pelo `OidcClient` como o valor do esquema `Bearer` do cabeçalho HTTP `Authorization`.\n"
"Este filtro pode ser registrado com implementações de cliente REST do MicroProfile injetadas no endpoint Quarkus atual, mas não está relacionado aos requisitos de autenticação deste endpoint de serviço.\n"
"Por exemplo, ele pode ser um endpoint público ou estar protegido com mTLS."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/security-authentication-mechanisms.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "In this scenario, you do not need to protect your Quarkus endpoint by using the Quarkus OpenID Connect adapter."
msgstr "Neste cenário, você não precisa proteger seu endpoint Quarkus usando o adaptador Quarkus OpenID Connect."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/security-authentication-mechanisms.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The `quarkus-resteasy-client-oidc-token-propagation` extension requires the `quarkus-oidc` extension.\n"
"It provides Jakarta REST `TokenCredentialRequestFilter`, which sets the OpenID Connect Bearer token or Authorization Code Flow access token as the `Bearer` scheme value of the HTTP `Authorization` header.\n"
"This filter can be registered with MicroProfile REST client implementations injected into the current Quarkus endpoint, which must be protected by using the Quarkus OIDC adapter.\n"
"This filter can propagate the access token to the downstream services."
msgstr ""
"A extensão `quarkus-resteasy-client-oidc-token-propagation` requer a extensão `quarkus-oidc`.\n"
"Ela fornece o `TokenCredentialRequestFilter` do Jakarta REST, que define o token Bearer do OpenID Connect ou o token de acesso do Authorization Code Flow como o valor do esquema `Bearer` do cabeçalho HTTP `Authorization`.\n"
"Este filtro pode ser registrado com implementações de cliente REST do MicroProfile injetadas no endpoint Quarkus atual, que deve ser protegido usando o adaptador Quarkus OIDC.\n"
"Este filtro pode propagar o token de acesso para os serviços downstream."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/security-authentication-mechanisms.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "For more information, see the xref:security-openid-connect-client.adoc[OpenID Connect client and token propagation quickstart] and xref:security-openid-connect-client-reference.adoc[OpenID Connect (OIDC) and OAuth2 client and filters reference] guides."
msgstr "Para obter mais informações, consulte os guias xref:security-openid-connect-client.adoc[Início rápido de cliente OpenID Connect e propagação de token] e xref:security-openid-connect-client-reference.adoc[Referência de cliente e filtros OpenID Connect (OIDC) e OAuth2]."

#. type: Title ==
